Hello David,

Ok, so this must be h1, and you&#39;re looking for your processors to appear 
in the web ui. Sounds like it should work. You might doublecheck that 
the compiled class files should be in the classpath, the correct 
Processor.options is used by the running heritrix, and your processors 
extend the right superclass (e.g. Extractor). One thing you could try is 
configuring them manually in order.xml and see if it works.

Noah

